reviewText: Like most people, I bought this for the Alice Cooper episode. Nowhere near as cool as when I was a little kid (but then again, nothing ever is). Fun piece of 70s nostalgia though. And the live Alice songs do rock.
my son loved it . HE COLLECTS THINGS OF aLICE cOOPER
I purchased this for my 4 and a half year old since alice cooper is his fav singer...  we both enjoyed this movie over and over again!!!  who doesn't enjoy anything by Jim Henson!?!
Totally funny & awesome video to have if you're an Alice Cooper fan!
With Vincent Price and Alice Cooper playing around with the Muppets, what could more fun.  A great Muppet edition.
